query:
/*+ NoHashJoin(kt t mi_idx) NoMergeJoin(kt mi_idx t mk) NoMergeJoin(kt mi_idx mk t k) NoMergeJoin(it2 k kt mi mi_idx mk t it1) */ select min(mi_idx.info) AS rating,
min(t.title) AS north_european_dark_production
from kind_type AS kt
inner join title AS t
on kt.id = t.kind_id AND kt.kind IN ('video game',
'tv series') AND t.production_year > 2008
inner join movie_info_idx AS mi_idx
on t.id = mi_idx.movie_id AND mi_idx.info < '7.1'
inner join movie_keyword AS mk
on t.id = mk.movie_id AND mk.movie_id = mi_idx.movie_id
inner join keyword AS k
on k.id = mk.keyword_id AND k.keyword IS NOT NULL AND k.keyword IN ('violence',
'based-on-comic',
'violence',
'father')
inner join info_type AS it2
on it2.id = mi_idx.info_type_id AND it2.info = 'rating'
inner join movie_info AS mi
on t.id = mi.movie_id AND mi.movie_id = mi_idx.movie_id AND mk.movie_id = mi.movie_id AND mi.info IN ('Sweden',
'America',
'Swedish',
'American',
'Bulgaria',
'Denish',
'USA',
'Norway',
'Norwegian',
'USA')
inner join info_type AS it1
on it1.id = mi.info_type_id AND it1.info = 'countries';
